entry.value: UPDATE mobifarm.loan_requests a SET a.code = '${t24_loanReference}', a.t24_loanReference = '${t24_loanReference}' where a.code = '${loanReferenceID}'

SELECT CONCAT(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(), ROUND(RAND() * 100000)) AS sessionId1, UUID() as sessionId, DATE_FORMAT(STR_TO_DATE(lr.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d %T'), '%Y%m%d') as loanValueDate, DATE_FORMAT(STR_TO_DATE(DATE_ADD(lr.created_on, INTERVAL 3 MONTH), '%Y-%m-%d %T'), '%Y%m%d') as loanMatDate, lr.code as loanReferenceID, "4001" as accountOfficer, 'KES' as currency, CONVERT(lr.loan_product_id,CHAR) as chargeCode, CONVERT(SUM(lf.rate),CHAR) AS chargeAmount, DATE_FORMAT(STR_TO_DATE(DATE_ADD(lr.created_on, INTERVAL 1 MONTH), '%Y-%m-%d %T'), '%Y%m%d') as loanTerm, CONVERT(lr.principal_amount,CHAR) AS transactionAmount, t24_customer_no as customerId, t24_account_no as drawDownAccount, lr.status FROM mobifarm.loan_requests lr LEFT JOIN loan_fees lf ON lr.loan_product_id=lf.loan_product_id Right JOIN users u on u.id = lr.member_id WHERE lr.sent_to_oracle=0 and u.t24_customer_no is NOT null and u.t24_account_no is NOT null and lr.status = 'RUNNING' or lr.status = 'APPROVED' GROUP BY lf.loan_product_id,lr.id
